**Description**:
PBJ `v0.10.0` generates real inner classes for inner Protobuf types. For example (pseudo-code):
```
message foo {
    message bar {
    }
}
```
will produce
```
public final class foo {
    public final static class bar {
    }
}
```
for all the generated code (model, codecs, schema, and tests) instead of creating separate top-level Java classes for each message.
